*Posebna* pažnja se posvećuje detetu. (Special attention is dedicated to the child.) 

Ne postoji *posebna* pravila o tome. (There are no special rules about it.) 

On je dobio *posebne* počasti. (He was given special honors.) 

Ona je izuzetno *posebna*. (She is exceptionally special.) 

*Posebno* se izdvajaju one koji su uspeli. (Those who succeed are singled out particularly.)